@3:00 pm!
Kiddos who wear Jurassic World(s) Dinosaur Mask (produced by Mattel) and have customized them to their will! Come along and play! Get to know eachother with some activities such as dancing, or doing some crafty stuff, or sharing tips and sharing tips/tricks or even taking photos! A commemorative tiktok video will be made at the end! 

Snacks end Drinks will be provided! (So long as we keep clean!)
